 Metafield object
 2024-04 latest
 Metafields enable you to attach additional information to a Shopify resource, such as a Product or a Collection. For more information about the Shopify resources that you can attach metafields to, refer to HasMetafields.
 On this page
 Fields
 Types that return Metafield
 Fields
 type (String!)
 The type of data that the metafield stores in the value field. Refer to the list of supported types.
 value (String!)
 The data to store in the metafield. The data is always stored as a string, regardless of the metafield's type.
